data.name: richTextBox1.Text
data.value:
Shoot left always to get the target to go up top! There is really nothing else to say. Keep shooting left and nudge the game a little when ball comes down to prevent ball from going straight down the middle.
The left "loop" advances bonus and if target goes up top you gain bonus multiplier as well. When at 5x you can shoot right loop instead. Rollovers gives points and lanes up top adds to bonus.
Shoot only targets if you happen to have 1-2 left. Awards multiplier.
